<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .email-container {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .case-pill {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #495057;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Data Erasure Confirmation</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
            <p>This is to confirm that your Right to Erasure (Right to be Forgotten) request has been successfully fulfilled.</p>
            
            <p><strong>Request Details:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Request ID: <span class="case-pill">{{caseId}}</span></li>
                <li>Completed On: {{completionDate}}</li>
            </ul>

            <p>In accordance with privacy regulations, we have permanently anonymized and scrubbed your personal data from our active processing systems, including your consent records and associated grievances.</p>
            
            <p>Please note that some data may persist in our immutable audit logs and system logs for regulatory compliance purposes, but it has been stripped of direct identifiers where possible.</p>

            <p>Thank you for choosing Proteccio for your privacy management.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated notification from the Proteccio Consent Management System.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
